### CHECKLIST — AUDIT LOG MODULE
### ============================================================
###
###  BLOCK 0 — Generate records
###  [ ] 0.1   GET users                         → 200
###  [ ] 0.2   GET projects                      → 200
###  [ ] 0.3   POST create user                  → 201 (triggers CREATE log)
###  [ ] 0.4   POST create task                  → 201 (triggers CREATE log)
###  [ ] 0.5   POST assign worker                → 201 (triggers ASSIGN log)
###  [ ] 0.6   PATCH status → in_progress        → 200 (triggers STATUS_CHANGE)
###  [ ] 0.7   PATCH status → in_review          → 200 (triggers STATUS_CHANGE)
###  [ ] 0.8   PATCH status → done               → 200 (triggers STATUS_CHANGE)
###  [ ] 0.9   DELETE user                       → 204 (triggers DELETE log)
###
###  BLOCK 1 — GET by entity
###  [ ] 1.1   GET task audit logs               → 200, multiple records
###  [ ] 1.2   GET user audit logs               → 200
###  [ ] 1.3   GET project audit logs            → 200
###  [ ] 1.4   GET assignment entity logs        → 200
###  [ ] 1.5   GET milestone entity logs         → 200
###  [ ] 1.6   GET page=1 limit=2                → 200, meta.limit = 2
###  [ ] 1.7   GET page=2 limit=2                → 200, next page
###  [ ] 1.8   GET default pagination            → 200, default page 1 limit 20
###  [ ] 1.9   GET entity with no records        → 200, empty array
###  [ ] 1.10  GET invalid entityType            → 400 enum error
###  [ ] 1.11  GET entityType is number          → 400
###  [ ] 1.12  GET entityId not UUID             → 400 UUID error
###  [ ] 1.13  GET page=0                        → 400
###  [ ] 1.14  GET page=-1                       → 400
###  [ ] 1.15  GET limit=0                       → 400
###  [ ] 1.16  GET limit=200                     → 400 exceeds max
###  [ ] 1.17  GET limit=101                     → 400 exceeds max
###  [ ] 1.18  GET page=first (string)           → 400
###
###  BLOCK 2 — GET by user
###  [ ] 2.1   GET manager logs                  → 200
###  [ ] 2.2   GET worker logs                   → 200
###  [ ] 2.3   GET deleted user logs             → 200, records still exist
###  [ ] 2.4   GET with pagination               → 200, meta block present
###  [ ] 2.5   GET user with no records          → 200, empty array
###  [ ] 2.6   GET userId not UUID               → 400
###  [ ] 2.7   GET empty userId                  → 400 or 404
###  [ ] 2.8   GET page=0                        → 400
###  [ ] 2.9   GET limit=500                     → 400
###
###  BLOCK 3 — Verify record content
###  [ ] 3.1   STATUS_CHANGE records have old + new values   → ✅
###  [ ] 3.2   CREATE + DELETE records for user              → ✅
###  [ ] 3.3   Meta block has correct structure              → ✅
###
### ✅ 36 requests — all passing = Audit Log module complete
